2026-03-29T11:43:17.5726003Z             "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- Moved email window settings (offset hours, window size, window count) from global-only configuration to per-customer overrides with global fallback — null values fall back to the global EmailSettings defaults\r\n- Added a per-customer \"Include Latest Locations\" toggle to control whether the Latest Locations section appears in the daily summary email\r\n- Combined the four separate update sections on the customer Detail page (Name, Timezone, Emails, Send Times) into a single unified \"Customer Settings\" form with one Update button\r\n- Added EF Core migration for the four new Customer columns (SummaryWindowOffsetHours, SummaryWindowHours, SummaryWindowCount, IncludeLatestLocations)\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n- `src/Hpoll.Data/Entities/Customer.cs` — added four new fields: SummaryWindowOffsetHours, SummaryWindowHours, SummaryWindowCount (nullable int), IncludeLatestLocations (bool)\r\n- `src/Hpoll.Data/Migrations/20260329071317_AddCustomerEmailSettings.cs` — EF Core migration adding the new columns with IncludeLatestLocations defaulting to true for existing rows\r\n- `src/Hpoll.Email/EmailRenderer.cs` — reads per-customer overrides from DB, falls back to global settings; conditionally renders Latest Locations section\r\n- `src/Hpoll.Admin/Pages/Customers/Detail.cshtml` — replaced 4 separate forms with one combined settings form; added inputs for window size, count, offset, and latest locations toggle\r\n- `src/Hpoll.Admin/Pages/Customers/Detail.cshtml.cs` — merged four POST handlers into single OnPostUpdateSettingsAsync; added BindProperty fields and validation for new settings; activity summary uses per-customer settings\r\n- `tests/Hpoll.Admin.Tests/` — updated unit and integration tests for the combined handler and new settings (529 tests passing)\r\n\r\n## Test Plan\r\n\r\n- [ ] Verify existing customers with no overrides (null values) continue using global defaults for window settings\r\n- [ ] Set per-customer window hours/count/offset and confirm the activity summary and email preview reflect the custom values\r\n- [ ] Toggle \"Include Latest Locations\" off and confirm the email preview omits the Latest Locations section\r\n- [ ] Verify the combined settings form saves all fields (name, timezone, emails, send times, window settings) in a single submit\r\n- [ ] Confirm validation errors (invalid email, invalid timezone, window hours < 1) prevent saving and display appropriate messages\r\n- [ ] Run full test suite: all 529 tests pass\r\n",
